<P align="center"><A name="rihabiri"></A><BR>
<FONT color="#ff0000">⑥</FONT>　<FONT color="#0000ff">「リハビリと私」</FONT><BR>
</P>
<CENTER>
<TABLE border="1" cellpadding="12" width="600">
